quran[15{c,v,t}:
70,40,"pas nahi, mein qasam khata hon mashriqon aur maghrabon ke maalik ki, hum iss par Qadir hain"
70,41,ke inn ki jagah inn se behtar log le ayen aur koi hum se baazi le jaane wala nahi hai
70,42,lehaza aِnhin apni behooda baton aur apne khail mein para rehne do yahan taq ke yeh apne uss din taq poanch jayen jis ka un se wada kya ja raha hai
70,43,jab yeh apni qabron se nikal kar iss terhan doray ja rahay hon ge jaisay apne buton ke asthanon ki taraf daud rahay hon
70,44,"inn ki nigehain jhuki hui hon gi, zillat inn par chhaa rahi hogi woh din hai jis ka inn se wada kya ja raha hai"
71,1,hum ne Nooh ko is ki qoum ki taraf bheja ( is hadaayat ke sath ) ke apni qoum ke logon ko khabardaar kar day qabal is ke ke un par aik dard naak azaab aeye
71,2,"a seen ne kaha"" ae meri qoum ke logo, mein tumahray liye aik saaf saaf khabardaar kardainay wala ( paighambar ) hon"
71,3,( tum ko aagah karta hon ) ke Allah ki bandagi karo aur is se daro aur meri itaat karo
71,4,"Allah tumahray gunaaho se dar guzar farmaiye ga aur tumhe aik waqt muqarrar taq baqi rakhay ga haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ka muqarrar kya howa waqt jab aa jata hai to phir taalla nahi jata kash tumhe iss ka ilm ho """
71,5,"uss ne arz kya"" ae mere rab, mein ne apni qoum ke logon ko shab o roz puraka"
71,6,magar meri pukaar ne unn ke faraar hi mein izafah kya
71,7,"aur jab bhi mein ne unn ko bulaya taakay to unhen maaf kar day, unhon ne kaanon mein ungelian thoons len aur apne kapron se mun dhaank liye aur apni rawish par urr gay aur bara taqqabur kya"
71,8,phir mein ne un ko hankay pukare (buland aawaz) dawat di
71,9,phir mein ne alania bhi un ko tableegh ki aur chupkay chupkay bhi samjhaya
71,10,"mein ne kaha apne rab se maffi mango, be shak woh bara maaf karne wala hai"
